\backslash
addcontentsline{toc}{section}{1.1 Purpose}
\end_layout

\end_inset

1.1 Description Of Given Problem
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
lettrine{T}{he purpose of }
\end_layout

\end_inset

this document is providing requirements and specifications about an application
 due to monitoring process done by city of Milan.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

The application will be called 'SmartCityAdvisor' and its scope will be
 provide to citizen more information about pubblic service situation, like
 hospital queues or parking availability, and to manage in the best possible
 way exceptional event like accidents, VIPs arrival or other, with a momentary
 traffic deviation.
 The objective of this project is improve the city life through a mobile
 application, that will allow to recive notifications about actual traffic
 situation or about momentary deviation, according to own GPS position,
 and also it will allow to check which is the empiest hospital in case of
 emergency or which is the best one for a precise emergency.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

As required by city of Milan, as new functionality i will propose the parking
 availability, that is possible with data already measured.: the idea is
 that citizens will indicate the destination in the mobile app and system
 will propose all the possible solutions with free place.
 A possible updating for parking situation should be each 10 minutes during
 the week ann each five minutes in the weekend or during festivities.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

The system also provides Application Programming Interface (API) to enable
 further developments.
\end_layout

