 to all users
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

It has been produced to be used via web or mobile application and it has
 a main page.
 Here you can use all the functionalities of the project and, if you want,
 you can log in for changing your profile infos or changing preferences
 about notifications.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

With a pc, on the top of the public page we could find six links that allow
 to navigate into the web site and below them we have the possibility to
 refine our search, we find a calendar and some statistics.
