\backslash
lettrine{I}{n the application}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 there aren't sensible information but, in order to ensure the maximum tranquili
ty to our users and in order that their trust in us, we want guarantee an
 high protected area.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The communications between server and clients must be completely secure
 and pro- tected by strong encryption such as SSL protocol.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
